HEADWORD: Parkeriaceae
<hw>Parkeriaceae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural family of ferns
coextensive with the genus <gen>Ceratopteris</gen>; sometimes it is
included in the family <fam>Polypodiaceae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
